{"tid":101652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南夢宮創始人中村雅哉先生逝世 享年91歲","createTime":"2017-01-31T04:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T04:18:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb9763fdc84e7373747317c5b32fc00677cbc14","tid":101652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:58:04.000Z","msg":"編輯:Septem 2017-01-31 12:52 來源:A9VG<br />\n萬代南夢宮於日前發表了訃告&mdash;&mdash;Namco創始人中村雅哉先生於2017年1月22日逝世，享年91歲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.a9vg.com//2017/01/31/1/99b75d75548dbd5b97bab4b3ad83631f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.a9vg.com%2F%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F1%2F99b75d75548dbd5b97bab4b3ad83631f.jpg&h=507aceee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中村先生出生於1925年12月24日，於1948年畢業於橫濱國立大學，並在1955年創立了中村製造、1977年更名為Namco。他於2002年出任Namco總裁，此後Namco在2005年和Bandai合併。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望中村先生一路走好。"},{"pid":"e6c997736f87173e337159ddd0c00bcffdcba275","tid":101652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd4d80c0ca53daf3ab614a7435eeac433f86675","tid":101652,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"食鬼之父 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e2ce97888f23b6c3142d9d3d15b197f77f085f","tid":101652,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"食毒L水食得最深既其中一間公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac92d65f29a18ba94522775918f05f54197e22c5","tid":101652,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食毒L水食得最深既其中一間公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce59578ddba8b2b8391c